Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.97,0:27:35.47,episode preview,Fag,0,0,0,,Let me tell a sad, sad story.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.47,0:27:36.55,episode preview,Fag,0,0,0,,No different than any other.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.55,0:27:37.96,episode preview,Fag,0,0,0,,What exactly does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.96,0:27:40.01,episode preview,Fag,0,0,0,,People only see us as deadbeats!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.01,0:27:41.43,episode preview,Fag,0,0,0,,By taking us at face value, it makes them all shallow!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.55,0:27:43.66,episode preview,Fag,0,0,0,,I'm not a shallow guy, so I'm not going to continue my rant!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.66,0:27:46.59,episode preview,Fag,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm just bitter... but you guys are keeping pretty sweet, right?
